Terms and Conditions & Privacy Policy

    Effective Date: 2025

I. Introduction

    Welcome to Doer, a social networking application designed to help users build habits, share progress, and connect with communities. These Terms and Conditions and Privacy Policy govern your use of the app and its related services. By using Doer, you agree to be bound by these terms. If you do not agree, please refrain from using the app.

    This document complies with the Data Privacy Act of 2012 (Republic Act No. 10173) and relevant laws and regulations of the Republic of the Philippines.

II. User Responsibilities

    1. You must be at least 13 years old to use this app.

    2. You are responsible for the content you post and your interactions with others.

    3. You agree not to use the app for any unlawful, harmful, or abusive activities.

III. User-Generated Content

    You retain ownership of content you upload but grant Doer a non-exclusive, royalty-free, transferable license to use, reproduce, distribute, and display such content within the app and affiliated services.

    You may not upload content that infringes on the intellectual property or privacy rights of others.

