    Doer collects the following data:

        a. Account Information: Name, email address, date of birth, username.

        b. Device Information: Device ID, IP address, browser type, OS.

        c. Usage Data: App activity, feature usage, session duration.

        d. Location Data: With user consent, approximate or precise location.

        e. Behavioral Data: Engagement with posts, likes, messages, etc.

    This data is used to:

        a. Provide personalized content and experiences.

        b. Improve the appâ€™s features and performance.

        c. Display relevant in-app advertisements.

        d. Monitor and prevent abuse or violations of the terms.

V. Data Sharing and Disclosure

    We may share your data:

        a. With third-party service providers (e.g., hosting, analytics, ads) under strict confidentiality agreements.

        b. If required by law, such as in response to a subpoena or court order.

