    We do not sell your personal data to third parties.

VI. Cookies and Tracking Technologies

    Doer uses cookies and similar technologies to:

         a. Maintain user sessions.

         b. Analyze trends and app usage.

         c. Deliver targeted content.

    Users can manage cookie preferences through their device settings.

VII. User Rights Under Philippine Law

    Under the Data Privacy Act of 2012, you have the right to:

         a. Access your personal data.

         b. Correct inaccurate or outdated data.

         c. Object to data processing.

         d. Withdraw consent at any time.

         e. Lodge a complaint with the National Privacy Commission (NPC).

    To exercise these rights, contact our Data Protection Officer at: JohnDoer@gmail.com.

VIII. Account Termination

